After you introduce Customer Success, we will coordinate the customer onboarding communication with the customer. We’ll include you and the SE as attendees on any calls/meetings for continuity and to ensure a smooth transition to the customer’s post-sale journey with Neo4j.

The Internal Debrief is a critical, brief meeting that prepares the Customer Success team with the proper background and intel that they will need to represent Neo4j in advising and advocating for this new customer. Please be prepared to address the following topics:

Key stakeholders - Project team, Project/initiative owner, Business Sponsor, Champion(s), etc.
Customer level of knowledge/skills
Use case, challenges, success criteria, milestones, etc.
Deal content confirmation, including any Professional Services


Prior to the Internal Debrief, the Customer Success Manager will review the Opportunity and linked Opportunity Doc (please ensure the Customer Success Manager has access to that document).

Thank you


